        <li class="login__list-item"><a href="https://community.usms.org/sso/login">Community/Forums</a></li>
        <li class="login__list-item"><a href="https://www.usms.org">USMS Website</a></li>
        <li class="login__list-item"><a href="https://www.usms.org/account/single-sign-out">Logout</a></li>
